OL,3,CPair 'tied up' by masked men in
OL,4,CMacosquin burglary
OL,6,FTwo people have been left 'badly
OL,7,Fshaken' after being 'tied up' by
OL,8,Fmasked men during a burglary near
OL,9,FColeraine.
OL,11,FShortly after 1 o'clock on Saturday
OL,12,Fmorning, two men entered a house in
OL,13,Fthe Formoyle Road area of Macosquin.
OL,15,FA man in his 70s and woman in her 60s
OL,16,Fwere ordered to hand over money and
OL,17,Fthe keys to a nearby vehicle were
OL,18,Ftaken.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
