OL,3,CPair 'tied up' by masked men in
OL,4,CMacosquin burglary
OL,6,FThe men drove off in a blue Nissan
OL,7,FJuke, which was last seen on the Moore
OL,8,FRoad in Londonderry shortly after 2am.
OL,10,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "At around
OL,11,F1:15am, it was reported that two
OL,12,Fmasked men entered a property in the
OL,13,Farea.
OL,15,F"It was reported that a man in his 70s
OL,16,Fand a woman in her 60s were tied up by
OL,17,Fthe men and ordered to hand over money.
OL,26,@rD@[OU
