PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F448A1779725464
OL,3,CPair 'tied up' by masked men in
OL,4,CMacosquin burglary
OL,6,F"The men left the property, taking two
OL,7,Fmobile phones, a watch and the keys
OL,8,Ffor a blue Nissan Juke that was parked
OL,9,Fnearby.
OL,11,F"The men drove off in the vehicle,
OL,12,Fwhich was last seen at the Moore Road
OL,13,Farea of Londonderry shortly after 2am.
OL,15,F"Both the male and female, who
OL,16,Falthough not injured, were left badly
OL,17,Fshaken following the incident."
OL,19,FAnyone with information that may
OL,20,Fassist enquiries is asked to contact
OL,21,Fpolice.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
